 214:app_statemachine.c **** // Lowest common ancestor (LCA) walk %========================================%
 215:app_statemachine.c **** // For a given state, walk up its parents to ROOT, then walk down to incoming
 216:app_statemachine.c **** // state. Allows for heirarchical and shared entry/exit behaviour.
